Definition: air moving (sometimes with considerable force) from an area of high pressure to an area of low pressure

Definition: a fruiting structure resembling an umbrella that forms the top of a stalked fleshy fungus such as a mushroom

Definition: a plant originally cultivated but now growing wild
Definition in Sorani: گیایەک کە لەئەسڵدا نراوە بەڵام ئێستە هەرزە

Definition: reproductive organ of angiosperm plants especially one having showy or colorful parts

Definition: the parts of a plant involved in its reproduction
Definition in Sorani: ئەو بەشانەی گیا کە لە زاوزێیدا دەخیلن

Definition: cosmopolitan herbaceous or woody plants with hollow jointed stems and narrow long-bladed leaves

Definition: a functional and structural unit of a plant or fungus
Definition in Sorani: بەشێکی کارکردی یان پێکهاتەیی گیا یان قارچێ

Definition in Sorani: گیایەک کە کاتێ دەستی لێ دەدرێ یان دەخورێ بە ئەندازەیەکی زۆر دەبێتە هۆی زیان کەوتن یان مەرگی هەر بوونەوەرێک

Definition in Sorani: گیایەک کە بافتی چێوی یان ئەندامی چێوی هەیە بەتایبەت ساق

a low woody perennial plant usually having several major branches

Definition in Sorani: گیایەک کە تاڕادەیەک یان یەکسەر لە ئاو دەژی چ ڕیشەکەی لە قوڕ بێ وەک

Synonyms: sum; sum of money; amount; amount of money;

Definition: money that is invested with an expectation of profit

Definition in Sorani: ئەو سەرمایەی بۆ وە دەست هێنانی سەرمایەی زۆرتر لە بەر دەستدا یە

Definition: the metal or paper medium of exchange that is presently used

Synonyms: consumption; economic consumption; usance; use; use of goods and services;
Definition: (economics) the utilization of economic goods to satisfy needs or in manufacturing
